response.original_title: Iggy Pop - Live at Sydney Opera House
response.overview: Hailed as the ‘Godfather of Punk’, Iggy Pop made his long-awaited Sydney Opera House debut in 2019 performing his genre-defining back-catalogue of hits, including songs from seminal albums Lust For Life, The Idiot, The Stooges’ albums as well as more recent works.
response.title: Iggy Pop - Live at Sydney Opera House
